    h3. Disclosure

    SublimeVideo may disclose personally identifiable information under special circumstances, such as to comply with subpoenas or when your actions violate the "Terms of Service":/terms.

    h3. Changes

    SublimeVideo may periodically update this policy. We will notify you about significant changes in the way we treat personal information by sending a notice to the primary email address specified in your SublimeVideo primary account holder account or by placing a prominent notice on our site.

